# Normalize line endings. This repo (and Godot's own output) is LF throughout,
# but contributors on Windows may have core.autocrlf=true globally, which
# mis-flags LF-only text files (notably *.png.import) as perpetually modified.
# Pinning eol=lf per-file makes git ignore autocrlf here and keeps status clean.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets: never touch line endings or try to diff as text.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.wav binary
*.ogg binary
*.mp3 binary
*.zip binary
